{"tid":1071814,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【中國人的女神】歐陽娜娜回應敏感政治問題：我為我身為中國人驕傲！","createTime":"2019-03-21T15:04:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-23T13:53:29.000Z","uid":231132,"like":5,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a758966de24badda651c64754890c323364d00bd","tid":1071814,"uid":231132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T15:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/images/0000-1553167534.jpg?crop=1.00xw:1.00xh;0,0&amp;resize=980:*\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhips.hearstapps.com%2Fhmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2F0000-1553167534.jpg%3Fcrop%3D1.00xw%3A1.00xh%3B0%2C0%26resize%3D980%3A%2A&h=3fcefd54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歐陽娜娜目前正在波士頓就讀伯克利音樂學院，過去長時間在中國發展事業的她就曾因爲字正腔圓的發音而被質疑「口音變了」、「北京腔很重」，政治對於明星來說一向都是敏感議題，能避則避。而今日父親歐陽龍因過去工作經歷而被指台獨，連帶女兒歐陽娜娜也被罵翻，使得歐陽娜娜的工作室和她本人都發文表明立場。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/images/螢幕快照-2019-03-21-下午7-24-55-1553167573.png?crop=1xw:1xh;center,top&amp;resize=480:*\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhips.hearstapps.com%2Fhmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2F%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2019-03-21-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%887-24-55-1553167573.png%3Fcrop%3D1xw%3A1xh%3Bcenter%2Ctop%26resize%3D480%3A%2A&h=d3b59fc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歐陽娜娜的工作室發文：<br />\n<br />\n歐陽娜娜女士已經年滿十八歲，有自己獨立的思考和意志。目前她以學生身份在海外求學。 歐陽娜娜女士於2019年元旦期間，曾與母親一同回到江西吉安老家祭祖，她一直堅定認為，自己是中國人，並堅定支持一個中國原則。 敬請各大網絡平台及用戶，停止對歐陽娜娜女士的惡意揣測，並停止傳播不實信息。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com/images/螢幕快照-2019-03-21-下午7-25-11-1553167573.png?crop=1xw:1xh;center,top&amp;resize=480:*\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhips.hearstapps.com%2Fhmg-prod.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2F%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2019-03-21-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%887-25-11-1553167573.png%3Fcrop%3D1xw%3A1xh%3Bcenter%2Ctop%26resize%3D480%3A%2A&h=ae069cfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而歐陽娜娜也轉發工作室文章，並寫下：<br />\n<br />\n作為一個在海外的留學生，常會被問Where do you come from? I come from China. 這是我的回答。我從小和外公外婆爺爺奶奶關係好，我是聽著四川話長大的，他們說人不管到哪裡都要記住自己的根。我為我身為中國人驕傲，我永遠記得我的祖籍是江西吉安，永遠記著在老家族譜上看到自己的名字時的那份感動。<br />\n<br />\n感動中國！！"},{"pid":"fdbe56b43857e72d4679387c94a5bb2e85d266d1","tid":1071814,"uid":62822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T15:10:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7573b1a83fb7985752054ea08c0bcdf5f51146bb","tid":1071814,"uid":231132,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdbe56b43857e72d4679387c94a5bb2e85d266d1","tid":1071814,"uid":62822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T15:10:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T15:20:31.000Z","msg":"中國強大了 歐陽娜娜歸宗認祖"},{"pid":"18b7fd7f0cc8c10d3a349f2e34008868d86356e9","tid":1071814,"uid":155818,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T15:21:06.000Z","msg":"乜水1"},{"pid":"421e0858e5f415112ba49c0568456322a49074cb","tid":1071814,"uid":191701,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T15:23:25.000Z","msg":"遲d又一名台灣女孩 北京你又見到一名台灣人大政協委員舉手"},{"pid":"2b9df5e8b8b254b16e492cb5a40e1e566e469edb","tid":1071814,"uid":231132,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"18b7fd7f0cc8c10d3a349f2e34008868d86356e9","tid":1071814,"uid":155818,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T15:21:06.000Z","msg":"乜水1"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T15:25:24.000Z","msg":"下一個連登女神<br />\nig: nanaouyang<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/nanaouyang?utm_source=ig_profile_share&amp;igshid=gh9xucc9dma8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fnanaouyang%3Futm_source%3Dig_profile_share%26igshid%3Dgh9xucc9dma8&d=tFviIiuTv25K9aUiQ%2BXN3Dv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=745dc958\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/nanaouyang?utm_source=ig_profile_share&amp;igshid=gh9xucc9dma8</a>"},{"pid":"dcf241d2a4f20ebe70cf195122ed98d46ef759c1","tid":1071814,